SELECT axis.*, ( WITH new_reports AS ( SELECT reports.id FROM reports INNER JOIN accounts ON accounts.id = reports.target_account_id WHERE date_trunc('day', reports.created_at)::date = axis.period AND accounts.domain IN (SELECT domain FROM instances WHERE reverse('.' || domain) LIKE reverse('.' || 'example.com'::text)) ) SELECT count(*) FROM new_reports ) AS value FROM ( SELECT generate_series(date_trunc('day', '2023-11-04 02:53:40.002463'::timestamp)::date, date_trunc('day', '2023-11-06 02:53:40.002628'::timestamp)::date, interval '1 day') AS period ) AS axis
